<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Safari Compatibility Test - ToolChest</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen">
    <div class="p-8 space-y-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--sand-100);">
                Safari Compatibility Test
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--neutral-400);">
                This page demonstrates the new Safari-compatible glass morphism system.
