                <strong>Chrome/Firefox:</strong> Glass morphism effects | 
                <strong>Safari:</strong> Solid backgrounds with perfect readability
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Test: New Glass Utility Classes -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6" style="color: var(--sand-200);">
                âœ… New Glass Utility Classes (Automatic Safari Compatibility)
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
